title: Flex Rent Payments, Patio/Balcony, Pet Friendly
neighborhood: 6640 North Humboldt Avenue, Minneapolis / St Paul, MN
posting_body: ['Located in the northeast portion of Brooklyn Center, north of Minneapolis and less than 1.5 miles west of the Mississippi River is Sterling Square Apartments.', 'The community boasts a mix of one, two, and three-bedroom apartments for rent in Brooklyn Center.', 'Sterling Square Apartments offers community amenities such as on-site laundry, a playground with a picnic area, garage parking, and controlled access.', 'Apartment highlights include patios/balconies and upgraded kitchens.', 'Our Brooklyn Center apartments are also pet-friendly, so you never have to decide between your furry friends and comfort again!', 'The community also benefits from convenient access to the Humboldt Ave N & 67th', 'Ave N Metro Transit bus stop positioned adjacent to the property.', 'We are located near Brooklyn Center High School and Brooklyn Center Police Department.', 'Call Sterling Square Apartments today to find the right home for you!', '-Picnic Area', '-Laundry Facilities', '-Flex Rent Payments', '-Air Conditioner', '-Patio/Balcony', '-Garages Available', '-Playground', '-Pet Friendly', '-Ceiling Fans', '-Online Payment Options', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'Monday-Friday: 9AM-5PM', '6640 North Humboldt Avenue, Minneapolis, MN 55430', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Equal Housing Opportunity.', 'Specials are based on availability and may expire or change at any time.', 'Specials and discounts may not be combined.', 'Rates are subject to change without advance notice.']
